videoSnippet.title: Journalist Christoph Rottwilm Gives Carlsen a Run for His Money
videoSnippet.description:

Magnus Carlsen vs Christoph Rottwilm
The 4th annual PlayLiveChallenge, Hamburg, Germany - Oct-08 
English Opening: Agincourt, Wimpey System (A13)

1. Nf3 d5 2. c4 e6 3. b3 Nf6 4. Bb2 c5 5. e3 Be7 6. cxd5 exd5 7. d4 b6 8. Bb5+ Bd7 9. Bxd7+ Nbxd7 10. O-O O-O 11. Nc3 Rc8 12. dxc5 Nxc5 13. Rc1 Re8 14. Qe2 Ne6 15. Rfd1 Bb4 16. Nb5 Rxc1 17.
